In these times of globalisation, the world reminds us that poverty and hunger, unrest and natural disasters in Africa or Asia also impact stability and standards of living in Europe or America.
However, beneficiary countries also need to demonstrate their capacity to properly manage the funds entrusted to them.
Maximum attention to the issue should come from the Members of Parliament, and from both the EU and from beneficiary States.
